value.0: Fashioned from rough-hewn wood, this simple door swings on ill-fitting hinges.

You cannot place any bags or containers with any items in them or you will lose the items and possibly the bag / container itself.

Do not put gold in this chest, use the bank!  (Or you will lose the gold!)

It is impossible to steal from this chest, and any of your characters can access the items from this container that you have placed in it.
